<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-us">
      <div class="bret-card" style="text-align:center;">
        <img src="images/bret-photo.svg" alt="Bret Swope, founder of AltaMedicare" class="bret-photo" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
        <h3>Bret Swope</h3>
        <p class="role">Founder &middot; Licensed Medicare Agent</p>
        <p style="color:var(--charcoal-soft);">Based in Orem, Utah</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-narrow" style="margin:0;">
        <h2>Why I Started AltaMedicare</h2>
        <p>I started AltaMedicare because I watched too many people in my own community struggle to make sense of Medicare. They&rsquo;d get bombarded with mailers, called by out-of-state agents who didn&rsquo;t know Utah, and pressured into plans that didn&rsquo;t actually fit their lives.</p>
        <p>My approach is different. I take the time to understand your situation, explain Medicare in plain English, and walk you through your options &mdash; without pushing you toward any particular plan. If a Medicare Supplement makes more sense for you than Medicare Advantage, I&rsquo;ll tell you. If your current plan is already a good fit, I&rsquo;ll tell you that too.</p>

        <h2>What You Can Expect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>An educational first.</strong> I want you to actually understand your options, not just sign something.</li>
          <li><strong>Local Utah knowledge.</strong> I know which doctors, hospitals, and pharmacies are in which networks &mdash; because I live here too.</li>
          <li><strong>No pressure, ever.</strong> If you need time to think, take time. If you want to bring a family member, please do.</li>
          <li><strong>Annual reviews.</strong> Plans change every year. I check in each fall to make sure yours still fits.</li>
          <li><strong>Help year-round.</strong> If you have a billing question in March or a prescription issue in July, I&rsquo;m here.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>My Mission</h2>
        <p>To make Medicare feel less confusing, less stressful, and less expensive for Utah families &mdash; one honest conversation at a time.</p>

        <div class="callout">
          <strong>Want to chat?</strong>
          <p style="margin:8px 0 0;">There&rsquo;s no cost, no obligation, and no high-pressure pitch. Just a real conversation about your Medicare options. Call <a href="tel:8013680700">(801) 368-0700</a> or <a href="contact.html">schedule a time</a> that works for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
